title: DAZ3D - Poser - Dial-a-Girl - Tokyo Edition for Genesis 2 Female
description:
Dial-a-Girl is back with another set of realistic character shaping presets!

This time we have five full character shapes from Japan (including one half-Japanese, half-European character; Maria).

Use the easy one-click system to mix-and-match full body, full face, breasts, cheeks, eyes, jaw & chin, mouth, nose and height presets to create distinctive and original characters.

Included are zero-shape presets should you wish to create any body section from scratch, or mix these presets with the original Dial-a-Girl product, or any other head or body morphs.

Also in Dial-a-Girl: Tokyo Edition are scaled head and height presets to make petite characters with Genesis 2 Female, from five-foot one to five-foot five.

The original Dial-a-Girl is NOT needed to use this product.

Poser Companion Files are included.
